<h1 id="how-to-use-it">How to use it?</h1>
<p>Ceramide are one of the <a href="https://www.sheenycare.com/active-ingredients-for-skin-care/" rel="dofollow" target="_blank">active ingredients</a> that is used to treat dry and sensitive skin. Hence, this ingredient is found in barrier repair creams and moisturisers.</p>

